Australia rugby union selectors
named the following team for the Wallabies’ season-opening Test
against Samoa on July 17 in Sydney:  15. Mark Gerrard                     
14. James O’Connor               
13. Adam Ashley Cooper        
12. Pat McCabe                      
11. Digby Ioane                      
10. Matt Giteau                       
9. Nick Phipps                         
8. Ben McCalman                
7. Matt Hodgson                      
6.  Rocky Elsom  (captain)                      
5. Nathan Sharpe                    
4. Sitaleki Timani                     
3. Ben Alexander                    
2. Stephen Moore                   
